Task 1 \'97 Project goal (one paragraph)\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf0 The 
\f0\b AI-Powered Playlist Creator
\f1\b0  is a React web app that turns a simple mood or moment into a ready-made music playlist. Instead of manually hunting for songs, a user just types something natural like 
\f2\i "chill Gujarati songs for a long drive"
\f1\i0  or 
\f2\i "high-energy gym mix,"
\f1\i0  and the app sends that prompt to the OpenAI API to brainstorm a themed song list, then matches those songs to real tracks (via a music API like Spotify/YouTube). Users can log in with Firebase, preview and refine the generated playlist, save it to their personal library, and share it with friends. The main goal is to remove the time and effort of building playlists by hand, giving anyone a personalized, mood-perfect playlist in a few seconds.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

