\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Task 4 \'97 Implementing "AI playlist generation" with React components + state\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf0 I'd build this feature around three components that share state by 
\f0\b lifting it up
\f1\b0  to a common parent.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f4 \cf0 \strokec2 App
\f1 \strokec2  (parent) owns the shared state with 
\f4 \strokec2 useState
\f1 \strokec2 : a 
\f4 \strokec2 prompt
\f1 \strokec2  string, a 
\f4 \strokec2 songs
\f1 \strokec2  array, and a 
\f4 \strokec2 loading
\f1 \strokec2  boolean. It passes data and callbacks down as props.\

\f4 \strokec2 MoodInput
\f1 \strokec2  (child) is a controlled text box plus a Generate button. It keeps the typed text in local state and, on submit, calls a 
\f4 \strokec2 onGenerate(prompt)
\f1 \strokec2  callback that 
\f4 \strokec2 App
\f1 \strokec2  passed to it. So the 
\f0\b data flowing up
\f1\b0  is the prompt string.\

\f4 \strokec2 PlaylistView
\f1 \strokec2  (child) receives the 
\f4 \strokec2 songs
\f1 \strokec2  array and 
\f4 \strokec2 loading
\f1 \strokec2  flag as 
\f0\b props from 
\f5 \strokec2 App
\f1\b0 \strokec2 . It maps over 
\f4 \strokec2 songs
\f1 \strokec2  to render a list of 
\f4 \strokec2 SongCard
\f1 \strokec2  components, or shows a spinner while 
\f4 \strokec2 loading
\f1 \strokec2  is true.\
The flow in code looks roughly like this:\
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f3 \cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 \
function App() \{\
  const [songs, setSongs] = useState([]);\
  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(false);\
\
  async function handleGenerate(prompt) \{\
    setLoading(true);\
    const res = await fetch("/api/generate", \{\
      method: "POST",\
      body: JSON.stringify(\{ prompt \}),\
    \});\
    const data = await res.json();   // \{ songs: [...] \}\
    setSongs(data.songs);\
    setLoading(false);\
  \}\
\
  return (\
    <>\
      <MoodInput onGenerate=\{handleGenerate\} disabled=\{loading\} />\
      <PlaylistView songs=\{songs\} loading=\{loading\} />\
    </>\
  );\
\}\
